('The Mad Monk', 'Boz', 'Admin District', '5', '20', '3', '-', '-', '[BM] Backup Request', '13000', '220', 'Boz Joins', 'Head to Vitriol Cesspool in Noctilum; Choose "Follow" for A, "Demand" for B; A: Continue; B: Gather 5 Muneria Flowers; Talk to Jejebba; Talk to Survivor; Defend against Heinous Blatta for 2 minutes; Defend against Heinous Forfex for 2 more minutes; Talk to Reggie; Talk to Eleonora', 'Choosing to ignore Jejebba results in him dying, and alters one of Boz''s later missions slightly. Enter the Vitriol Cesspool during the day, the Logi Blatta will aggro at night. Hug the west wall as you approach the survivor to avoid the Falsaxum noticing you. If you''re defeated during the second wave, you don''t have to redo the first. You can sprint in circles around the Forfexes to stall for some time.'),
